<!DOCTYPE html>
<html >
<head >
    <meta charset="utf-8" >
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" >
    <title >RW API - Twitter account migration</title >
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" >
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,700" media="all" >
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/foundation/6.2.3/foundation-flex.min.css"
          media="all" >
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.6.3/css/font-awesome.min.css"
          media="all" >
    <style >
        body {
            font-family: "Open Sans", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f6f6f6;
        }

        #main {
            height: 100vh
        }

        a {
            color: <%= application.principalColor %>;
        }

        .login-form {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px 60px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
        }

        .align-center {
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .row {
            align-items: center
        }

        .text-small {
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style >
</head >
<body >
<div class="row align-middle align-center" id="main" >
    <div class="small-12 columns" >
        <div class="row align-center" >
            <div class="small-10 medium-8 large-8 columns" >
                <div class="login-form row" >
                    <% if (error && error.length > 0) { %>
                        <div class="small-12 medium-10 large-10 columns columns align-center" >
                            <div class="callout alert" data-closable >
                                <p ><%= error %></p >
                                <button class="close-button" aria-label="Dismiss alert" type="button" data-close >
                                    <span aria-hidden="true" >&times;</span >
                                </button >
                            </div >
                        </div >
                    <% } %>
                    <div class="small-8 medium-8 large-5 columns align-center" >
                        <img src="<%= application.logo %>" >
                    </div >
                    <div class="small-10 medium-8 large-6 columns align-center" >
                        <h2 >Twitter account migration</h2 >
                        <p >Using Twitter to log in to <%= application.name %> is no longer supported. Using this
                            migration tool, you will be able to migrate your Twitter-based <%= application.name %>
                            account to use an email address and password for login. To start the migration process,
                            click the "Twitter" button below to log in using your existing Twitter-based account.</p >
                        <p class="text-small" >If you experience any issue in this process,
                            please send an email to <a target="_blank"
                                    href="mailto: resourcewatch@wri.org?subject=Twitter%20migration%20error&body=I%20am%20experiencing%20issues%20with%20the%20Twitter%20migration%20for%20my%20RW%20API%20account.%20Here%20are%20my%20details%3A%0A%0ATwitter%20username%2Fhandle%3A%20%0AEmail%20address%20I%27d%20like%20to%20associate%20with%20my%20account%20going%20forward%3A%0AThe%20error%20message%20I%27m%20seeing%2C%20or%20the%20issue%20I%27m%20experiencing%3A" >resourcewatch@wri.org</a >
                            with the subject "Twitter migration error".
                            In your email, include your Twitter username/handle, the email address you'd like to
                            associate with your account going forward, and
                            the error message you're currently seeing.</p >
                        <div class="third-party" >
                            <a href="/auth/twitter/auth?origin=<%= app %>" ><i class="fa fa-twitter"
                                                                               aria-hidden="true" ></i >Twitter</a >
                        </div >
                    </div >

                </div >
            </div >
        </div >
    </div >
</div >
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.2.4/jquery.min.js" ></script >
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/foundation/6.2.3/foundation.min.js" ></script >
</body >
</html >
